This Directory Is for BSB30415 course material.





This is a simulated assessment task.  
In this assessment task you will be required to listen to the customers request on the following slide and offer a solution to the customer by leaving a message on their answering service in the last slide.
Before responding to the customer please ensure you review the availability of the technicians by using the Bushland Blooms intranet (details in your full assessment guide). 
You also need to adhere to call principles at Bushland Blooms when leaving a voice message (details in your full assessment guide).

